channel.title: I am distraught
channel.description: Hello, i have set up my class path variable and it works just fine. However, this is not the case with the Path variable. I erase whats in the path variable and put in: C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_06\bin; then i go to command prompt and type in 'javac' and it works, but when i type in 'ipconfig' it doesnt work. So then i set it back to normal and 'javac' doesnt work but 'ipconfig' does. HELP

item.description:

if defined p (%p% -cp . *.java)
if defined p (goto end)
:error

:end
echo Finished!
